{"tid":329954,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"挪威係唔係到到都碌到卡?","createTime":"2017-07-20T18:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T13:47:25.000Z","uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0ba70c74f60fb4c6da92f761e2f54982a9619d","tid":329954,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T18:46:10.000Z","msg":"如題， 因為身上現金唔太多，想問下係挪威係咪到到都碌到卡<br />\n係丹麥試過去食飯唔比碌卡 結果攪到要問人借一舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fad1bdd2f8e963ef97cce0705368a853be8b355","tid":329954,"uid":12630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T18:48:51.000Z","msg":"其實好多地方都得 但點都好 帶少少現金傍身"},{"pid":"60318646427ce4fc0a6851893a3dd459e5f3696a","tid":329954,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:01:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實好多地方都得 但點都好 帶少少現金傍身</blockquote><br />\n就係唔多錢係身 得200蚊EUR  但仲要去芬蘭 所以想盡量兌少D過去"},{"pid":"efe2421da219391a84406e43648a3a06aeb6aaf8","tid":329954,"uid":12630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T14:58:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實好多地方都得 但點都好 帶少少現金傍身</blockquote><br />\n就係唔多錢係身 得200蚊EUR  但仲要去芬蘭 所以想盡量兌少D過去</blockquote><br />\nNorway 唔係到到都收euros 架..."},{"pid":"0d258e9c57f9db9e545d0402f011d2bf6da0756d","tid":329954,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"連火車站 locker 都收卡<br />\n<br />\n便利店，KFC, McDonald's 自助機都用卡。<br />\n<br />\n坐機場火車用 app 買。<br />\n<br />\n轉機留過半日，冇換過錢。"},{"pid":"73210ff5fa99a6133e5fdf899c9479d527fe0aac","tid":329954,"uid":98836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T15:05:56.000Z","msg":"去挪威5日<br />\n$1 cash都無換過用過<br />\n全程碌卡"},{"pid":"b6703ef9d0e32fdaa3510db60bac33d8aed24102","tid":329954,"uid":98836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T15:06:45.000Z","msg":"係歐洲食飯無得碌卡直接換下間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8d97022d8fe0af1eece34fdbd2f01e535e5a9e","tid":329954,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T15:26:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實好多地方都得 但點都好 帶少少現金傍身</blockquote><br />\n就係唔多錢係身 得200蚊EUR  但仲要去芬蘭 所以想盡量兌少D過去</blockquote><br />\nNorway 唔係到到都收euros 架...</blockquote><br />\n所以咪攞eur 兌nok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be495236216731915ee61ec1a3615386b1882628","tid":329954,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T15:28:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連火車站 locker 都收卡<br />\n<br />\n便利店，KFC, McDonald's 自助機都用卡。<br />\n<br />\n坐機場火車用 app 買。<br />\n<br />\n轉機留過半日，冇換過錢。</blockquote><br />\n我係丹麥車站買火車飛   d機係收卡 但插左卡入去要打pin  要簽名比卡就要去排隊人手買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23efea589c7b6eb421a3ec57a27cccaa7cc89a65","tid":329954,"uid":98836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T15:41:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連火車站 locker 都收卡<br />\n<br />\n便利店，KFC, McDonald's 自助機都用卡。<br />\n<br />\n坐機場火車用 app 買。<br />\n<br />\n轉機留過半日，冇換過錢。</blockquote><br />\n我係丹麥車站買火車飛   d機係收卡 但插左卡入去要打pin  要簽名比卡就要去排隊人手買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個pin 你可以入返信用卡係香港平時提款個pin<br />\n無可以去銀行set 返個"},{"pid":"2cc700882dbf6e26583b9a16c3b4dec3b1c7a207","tid":329954,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連火車站 locker 都收卡<br />\n<br />\n便利店，KFC, McDonald's 自助機都用卡。<br />\n<br />\n坐機場火車用 app 買。<br />\n<br />\n轉機留過半日，冇換過錢。</blockquote><br />\n我係丹麥車站買火車飛   d機係收卡 但插左卡入去要打pin  要簽名比卡就要去排隊人手買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有APP 買果啲盡量用APP買<br />\n<br />\n我張VISA 無密碼，都係求其入0000 就可以喺挪威租到LOCKER，喺波蘭自助售票機買到火車票，增值電話卡。"},{"pid":"b29cd7a3baf6efea5f4621fce550961f34b8cddc","tid":329954,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T03:24:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b6c004731cbccb2274ff8689eb0c1a6a878ff86","tid":329954,"uid":33961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T03:27:40.000Z","msg":"除左搭巴士之外(唔用 pass 既話) 都未試過用cash<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36fbfd0858bc5089d78cb978c10376e19540203","tid":329954,"uid":8414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:22:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左搭巴士之外(唔用 pass 既話) 都未試過用cash<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴士可以係app用信用卡俾錢,上車show俾司機睇"},{"pid":"ed431fc5bf6cbe92d3eaa60933cafd453f239a5e","tid":329954,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:47:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我真係1蚊nok都無唱<br />\n<br />\n係挪威原來真係有野一定要cash<br />\n依加坐緊程係挪威既巴士 係無得上網買飛 車上無得碌卡 好在佢收eur 但因為無錢找收貴左少少   不過好在有得比eur 唔係收左皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}